@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_jimbqd(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (0.29 / (v0 / (v1 + 0.54 / tmp + 0.04)))
    tmp = ((wp.exp(v1 + 0.73) - v0) * (wp.abs(v2 + 0.05) - wp.cos(v0 + 0.23)))
    tmp = 0.83
    v0 = (v0 * (wp.exp(v1 + 0.22) / 0.55))
    tmp = wp.sin((v2 * (v0 + 0.52 * v2 + 0.32)))
    v2 = (v0 - (tmp + wp.cos(v0 + 0.23)))
    data[tid] = v0
